test_zero_range:
assert [86, 87, 88, 89] == []
  Left contains 4 more items, first extra item: 86
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [86, 87, 88, 89]
test_large_range:
assert [] == [88, 89, 90]
  Right contains 3 more items, first extra item: 88
  Full diff:
  - [88, 89, 90]
  + []
test_even_range:
assert [87, 89] == [176, 178, 180]
  At index 0 diff: 87 != 176
  Right contains one more item: 180
  Full diff:
  - [176, 178, 180]
  + [87, 89]
